<P>
HOME TRUTHS ABOUT LIFE IN TWO BIG CITIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Re "The Big Move" (May 23): As an ex-Californian now living in New York, every 
day I'm asked why someone like me would be crazy enough to move from Los 
Angeles to New York (after all, most people move from East to West). I probably 
am crazy, but if you're not crazy, you don't belong here. 
</P>
<P>
SUSAN MOSS 
</P>
<P>
New York, N.Y. 
</P>
