HEALTH; MEDICAL CARE -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS; 
LABOR CODE VIOLATIONS; CANO, SALVADOR; SANTA INES MEDICAL ENTERPRISES INC 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
