<P>
JET CRASHES IN FOG; 4 HURT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
UNALAKLEET, Alaska 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A MarkAir jet crashed seven miles north of here Saturday, injuring the four 
crew members, the FAA said. The Boeing 737 was making a second landing approach 
in fog when the accident occurred. 
</P>
</TEXT>
