<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALL ABOARD SAFE AS ENGINE FIRE BREAKS OUT ON JETLINER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BOSTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
All aboard, 148 passengers and crew, were evacuated unharmed early Friday after 
an engine fire broke out as their TWA L-1011 jetliner taxied to a terminal at 
Boston's Logan International Airport, an airport spokesman said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
