cars, left, ; Photo, And Leigh Anne Hanloh, above, fine tunes the dragster she 
races. ; Photo, TOYS FOR ADULTS: Craig and Leigh Anne Hanloh, above, of 
Monrovia manufacture custom-built "sandrails" -- dune buggies without 
fiberglass covering their tubular frames of stainless steel. 
</P>
