Angeles Times; Photo, Producers Richard and Lili Zanuck threw a party for Kim 
Wozencraft, center, to introduce her to Hollywood. They paid $1 million for 
rights to her novel. MICHAEL JACOBS; Photo, Literary agents Lynn Pleshette and 
