over Democrats in terms of voter registration, includes most of Kern and San 
Luis Obispo counties, part of northern Los Angeles County, including Lancaster, 
and all of Inyo County., MATT MOODY / Los Angeles Times ; Photo, Wm. Thomas ; 
Photo, Gregory ; Photo, Reid 
</P>
