</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"It's young, fast, sexy and healthy. That's exactly the kind of association a 
beer company or taco maker is looking for." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Tim Blumenthal, an editor for Bicycling magazine in Emmaus, Pa., commenting 
on Taco Bell and Miller Brewing's use of cycling themes in their advertising. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060390-0126 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 228314 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 3, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
