Saturday's loss to Jacksonville (Ala.) State in the NCAA Division II baseball 
championship game. ; Photo, Assistant coach Rick Vanderhook and teammate mike 
Solar quickly come to the aid of Hodgins, who refused to leave the game. GEORGE 
