<TEXT>
<P>
As a 22-year resident of Yorba Linda, I was encouraged by the findings of the 
recent survey done by The Times in regards to Measure A, the Centralized Jail 
Initiative ("Voters Oppose Measure to Restrict Jail to Santa Ana," May 29). 
</P>
