<DOCNO> LA060390-0228 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 228871 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 3, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Real Estate; Part K; Page 18; Column 1; Real Estate Desk 
